SIMPLE: usurious
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Usurious
<hw>U*su"ri*ous</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Usury</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Practicing usury; taking illegal or exorbitant
interest for the use of money; <as>as, a <ex>usurious</ex>
person</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Partaking of usury; containing or involving usury;
<as>as, a <ex>usurious</ex> contract</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>U*su"ri*ous*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>U*su"ri*ous*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Usurp</ent>⟦br⟧
